data.oai_dc:dc: This is a Microsoft Excel (c) spreadsheet containing the raw data for JoH ID JOH-2011-107.R2. Column headings are self explanatory and have comments attached to the header cells. Data contained in columns I to AA represents area for CHC peaks 1-19 as quantified from chromatograms and data in columns AC to AU is the area expressed in proportional values after dividing by the pentadecane standard (peak 1).
